              </p>
            </li>

            <li>
              <p>
                Below is a histogram showing the distribution of <m>\hat{p}_{sim}</m> in 10,000 simulations under the null hypothesis. Estimate the p-value using the plot and determine the conclusion of the hypothesis test.
                <image width="85%" source="images/egypt.png" />
              </p>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </p>
      </statement>
